Privacy Policy

Last updated: January 2026

Kurapika is a Discord moderation bot. This Privacy Policy explains how data is collected and used.

Data Collected:
Kurapika may collect and store the following data strictly for functionality purposes:
- User IDs
- Server (Guild) IDs
- Channel IDs
- Role IDs
- Moderation logs and configuration settings

Kurapika does NOT collect or store message content.

Purpose of Data Collection:
The collected data is used only to:
- Perform moderation actions
- Maintain server-specific configurations
- Ensure proper and secure bot functionality

Data Sharing:
Collected data is never sold, shared, or transferred to third parties.

Data Retention:
Data is stored only for as long as necessary to provide the botâ€™s features and may be deleted at any time.

User Rights:
Server owners or administrators may request data removal by contacting the bot owner.

By using Kurapika, you consent to this Privacy Policy.
